data.description: Welcome to 3562 Oro Grande Blvd! This beautiful Havasu home is located on the south side of LHC, up the street from Oro Grande Middle School, and only 10 minutes from the Riviera boat launch. This meticulously well-kept home includes numerous upgrades, such as the additional room in the garage with a mini-split AC unit, sink, cabinetry, and more! A mini-split AC unit was installed in the master. Both the master and living room were wired for surround sound. Numerous fixtures were updated. Misters were installed above the hot tub, which conveys with the home. The home includes 2 utility/storage sheds, with one wired for electricity and the other wired for both electricity and water. Electric cooktop was replaced with natural gas. The water heater runs on natural gas with electric hookup as an option. Security screens were installed on all doors. Side parking with full RV hookups available on both sides of the home. Side parking on the left side of the home is 16 feet wide and 55+ feet deep, with even more parking available around back. The garage includes a mini-split AC unit, new cabinets and sink, and insulated garage doors and walls. Some furniture available outside of escrow.
